    "user_id": "U002CARLOS"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Got beautiful sungolds and an early run of Jimmy Nardellos out of a farm near Summerville. Cherokee Purples are coming in strong too.",
