    "ts": "1759391027.000200",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Jimmy Nardellos — yeah ok, I'll take what you got. Margaux's gonna make me rewrite the crudo but honestly those are probably better than what we had anyway.",
    "thread_ts": "1759390753.000000",
    "ts": "1759391164.000300",
    "user_id": "U002CARLOS"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "I'll do 10 lbs sungolds, 8 lbs Nardellos, split the Cherokee Purple order. Same price as your heirloom contract.",
    "thread_ts": "1759390753.000000",
    "ts": "1759391301.000400",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "works. can you hit us by 2pm Tuesday? doing mise en place review right after and I want to touch the product before the 3 o'clock briefing.",
