    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "lol say that to Margaux when I'm explaining why the crudo changed two days before service 😂 appreciate you Carlos, for real.",
