  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "yo Marco heads up — the 86 on the agnolotti is gonna bite us tonight. Margaux just confirmed a 74-cover count and I clocked at least three tickets last week where we ran dry by 9pm. bump the pasta batch by 30%",
    "thread_ts": "1759390753.000000",
