    "ts": "1759392123.001000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "checked — 3 flats and like 8 loose. I'll text Coastal Provisions and see if they can drop before 2",
    "thread_ts": "1759390753.000000",
    "ts": "1759392260.001100",
    "user_id": "U003MARCO"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "perfect. also Margaux moved the 3pm briefing to 3:15 so you got a little breathing room on the sauce réduc",
