    "ts": "1759392397.001200",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "lol 15 extra minutes might actually save my life today. you want me to split the extra batch or keep it as one big bowl?",
